name: The Showcase: #9 Bitcoin Over 9000! Shirt
description:
The ninth Tshirt in our showcase. A collection of 200 different 1/1 Tshirts in total made by DoYouCrypto. Be ready to experience the old and new crypto history. #9 Bitcoin Over 9000! 

Inspired by the over 9000 Dragonball Z scene. 
Do you remember the first time bitcoin broke $9000? We definitely do!
